s der Herkunftsprovinz Catania verglichen, um dialektale, innovative sowie kontaktbedingte Merkmale des Italienischen in der Migration beschreiben zu können. Auf der Webseite des Verlages werden zusätzlich Transkriptionen und Sprechproben aus dem RuhrCat-Korpus zur Verfügung gestellt (siehe Links im Tab Überblick bzw. Overview).  aThis study focuses on the spoken language of Italian-speaking inhabitants of the Ruhr Area. It offers an objective, quantifiable presentation of the differences in the forms of speech in pronunciation and prosody and examines the language spoken by Italians in the Ruhr Area in terms of phonetic and prosodic variations compared to Italian speakers in the province of Catania.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aGrammar, Comparative and generalxPhonetics. 0aItalian languagexPhonetics. 0aItalian languagexSpoken ItalianzGermanyzRuhr (Region). 0aItalian languagexSpoken Italian. 0aItalian languagezGermanyzRuhr (Region)xPhonetics. 0aItalian languagezGermanyzRuhr (Region)xSpoken Italian. 0aItalian languagezGermanyzRuhr (Region)zPhonetics. 0aItalian languagezItalyzCataniaxPhonetics. 0aItalian languagezItalyzCataniaxSpoken Italian. 0aItalian languagezSpoken ItalianzItalyzCatania. 4aGesprochenes Italienisch. 4aKontrastive Linguistik. 4aMigrationsvarietät. 4aProsodie. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / Phonetics & Phonology.2bisacsh  aMigrational Variety.  aSpoken Italian.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2015 Part 1z978311076251808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACK